name: ChickenBF
body:
### ChickenBF - JavaScript Brainfuck Interpreter

A doodle project for me to experiment with language and JavaScript optimisation. The design goal is to make an online Brainfuck IDE with debugger that also performs as efficiently as JavaScript allows.

The [Wiki](https://github.com/elpollouk/ChickenBF/Wiki) contains more in depth technical details.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
